Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.75,0:00:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,[theme music playing]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.91,0:01:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,MAKESHIFT
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.38,0:01:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ooi]\NWell then, let's begin tonight's meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.25,0:01:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] There's supposed to be eight\Nof them, but only seven are present.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.38,0:01:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That must mean that...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.55,0:01:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] They probably killed one\Nof their members.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.64,0:01:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,[Soichiro] Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.76,0:01:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ooi] In order to further the growth\Nof the Yotsuba Group
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.43,0:01:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,and best serve its financial interests,\Nwho should we kill next?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.18,0:01:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,[all gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.14,0:01:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You see? It's just like I told you\Nlast week!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.56,0:01:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] This is not good. At this rate...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.27,0:01:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ooi] But before we get to that,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.69,0:01:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,there are several topics\Nthat we need to discuss.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.57,0:01:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,First, there is the issue\Nof Hatori's death.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.28,0:02:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[Namikawa] That was unavoidable.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.33,0:02:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,To be honest, in a certain sense,\NI'm relieved that Hatori's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.00,0:02:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Kira has demonstrated that we must\Nbe committed to these meetings.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.67,0:02:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We now know what will happen\Nif we try to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.71,0:02:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ooi grunts softly]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.79,0:02:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we all understand what Hatori's\Ndeath means for the rest of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.26,0:02:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's not take it lightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.47,0:02:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, moving on. Our next topic\Nis Eraldo Coil's report…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.80,0:02:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,[all gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.89,0:02:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,One of their members just died\Nand that's all they're going to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.85,0:02:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So did we really pay five million dollars\Nfor this report?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.73,0:02:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, come on. Look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.57,0:02:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He hasn't found out anything important\Nabout L like his name or his face.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.49,0:02:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this Coil guy seriously going\Nto be of any use to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.49,0:02:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.16,0:02:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,There is something very interesting\Nin the last part of this report.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.66,0:02:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Coil's warning us that we can't afford\Nto take L's existence too lightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.00,0:02:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,In particular, it says, "The concentration\Nof killings that are beneficial to Yotsuba
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.76,0:02:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,will likely be noticed by L
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.68,0:03:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,if they continue on Fridays\Nand Saturdays."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.89,0:03:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds like this Eraldo Coil\Nhas figured out what we've been up to.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.44,0:03:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I admit, it's quite impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.56,0:03:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,At any rate, I personally think\Nwe should stop killing every weekend.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.94,0:03:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,This is unbelievable. It's like they're\Ntrying to confess to everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.28,0:03:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm, as long as we have this video\Nas evidence,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.20,0:03:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,we could probably arrest\Nall seven of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.29,0:03:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] This is not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.75,0:03:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Kira hasn't been flexible\Nup till now, has he?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.71,0:03:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be nice if he could spread out\Nhis killings over the whole week.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.42,0:03:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The fact that Coil noticed\Nwhat we've been up to
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.80,0:03:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,makes it dangerous to continue killing\Nat our usual pace.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.01,0:03:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,From now on,\Nwe have to be even more careful
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.34,0:03:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and make sure that nobody else happens\Nto notice a trend in these deaths.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.01,0:03:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, onto the main topic.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.18,0:03:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Who should we kill?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.94,0:03:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,[Soichiro sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.61,0:03:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we should focus on ELF Insurance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.82,0:04:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If they expand into the Japanese market,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.99,0:04:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yotsuba and many other companies\Nwill lose valuable clients to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.66,0:04:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,[Higuchi] Agreed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.95,0:04:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright. Any objections to killing these\Npeople from ELF with accidental deaths?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.75,0:04:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,[all] No objections.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.91,0:04:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,-Ah.\N-Is this for real?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.87,0:04:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,How can they do this so easily?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.13,0:04:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ooi] Another potential candidate\Nis Sentara Zenzai,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.34,0:04:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,a member of the Kugisawa Group.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.96,0:04:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,He's been protesting\NYotsuba's resort development plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.51,0:04:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Zenzai's known to have\Nhigh blood pressure,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.60,0:04:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,so we can designate a time\Nfor him to suffer a stroke,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.26,0:04:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,resulting in natural death.\NAny objections?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.81,0:04:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,-[Yotsuba Group] No objections.\N-[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.60,0:04:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Kira? Deaths by accident? By disease?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.52,0:04:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Designated times of death?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.98,0:04:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all just as we suspected.\NWe were right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.82,0:04:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Unfortunately, we can only be\Ncompletely sure
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.66,0:04:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,after those people they've named are dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.70,0:04:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[both gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.83,0:04:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] We will continue\Nto monitor these meetings
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.95,0:04:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and take note of what they say,\Nhow they act, and most importantly,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.29,0:04:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,whether the people they choose\Nactually die.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.83,0:05:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,If we can confirm the connection\Nbetween their plans and the deaths,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.38,0:05:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,then we'll definitely be able\Nto catch Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.42,0:05:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,-[both] Ryuzaki!\N-[L grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.76,0:05:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it? There's no need\Nto yell in unison.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.35,0:05:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't carry on\Nknowing these people will die!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.18,0:05:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,-That's just immoral!\N-Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.02,0:05:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] Here it comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.52,0:05:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you're planning to catch Kira\Nby letting these guys
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.27,0:05:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,actually carry out these murders,\Nbut... we can't let that happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.15,0:05:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. It's obvious that these\Nseven men are behind the killings.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.36,0:05:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,With Matsuda's testimony\Nand this footage we've recorded,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.53,0:05:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,we have all the evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.95,0:05:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] You're making this difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.95,0:05:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If we were to take action now,\Neverything we've done would go to waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.42,0:05:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ooi] So, what do you say we take care\Nof the ELF in three weeks,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.13,0:05:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and as for Zenzai, we'll ask Kira\Nto kill him this weekend?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.97,0:05:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[all] No objections.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.38,0:05:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's what they're going to do,\Nthen there's not much time left.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.85,0:05:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Light, we already know the phone numbers\Nof these board members, don't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.72,0:05:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.93,0:05:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care who we call.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.52,0:06:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to reach one of these men\Nand have them stop these murders.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.77,0:06:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] Please, hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.77,0:06:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That would cause suspicion.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.65,0:06:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It would mean the investigation\Ncaught up to them
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.15,0:06:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,three days after they were contacted\Nby Aiber.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.66,0:06:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, it would make it far more unlikely\Nthat we would be able to discover
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.95,0:06:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,who the real Kira might be.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.79,0:06:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't afford such a huge setback\Nseeing how far we've come.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.13,0:06:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[slurping]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.59,0:06:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to catch Kira…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.55,0:06:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,we're going to need some solid proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.22,0:06:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryuzaki, if one of these seven men\Nis in fact Kira,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.18,0:06:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,would it be safe to say that if I tried\Ncalling one of them,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.06,0:06:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,the odds of that person actually being\NKira is going to be one in seven?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.57,0:06:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm thinking there could be more\Nthan one Kira among them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.78,0:06:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,A probability of two in seven at most.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.15,0:06:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If we're prepared to let them know\Nthat the investigation
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.82,0:06:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,is catching up to them...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.78,0:06:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,let's place our bets on these odds.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.95,0:06:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryuzaki, I'm going to pose as L.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.16,0:07:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And judging from their conversation\Nso far, the one least likely to be Kira
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.00,0:07:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,but with the most influence is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.42,0:07:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,-[L and Light] Namikawa.\N-[Matsuda] Is Ooi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.13,0:07:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[Matsuda groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.13,0:07:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] If you're going to make a call,\Nplease use this phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.84,0:07:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's set up, so it can't be traced\Nor tapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.68,0:07:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,[Higuchi] You know, this would all go\Na lot faster if we kill off the execs
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.02,0:07:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,of our rival companies\Nand be done with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.60,0:07:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[Mido] That would be going\Na little too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.23,0:07:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,CALL FROM ANONYMOUS
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.31,0:07:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,[Higuchi] Why? We could kill them\Nand split their holdings.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.44,0:07:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light's voice distorted]\NIs this Reiji Namikawa,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.15,0:07:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,head of the Yotsuba Group's\NMarketing Department?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.99,0:07:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm. Yes, and who is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.28,0:07:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Listen carefully,\Nbut don't draw attention to yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.49,0:07:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I am L.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.79,0:07:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.67,0:07:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] I've planted cameras and wiretaps\Naround that meeting room.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.88,0:07:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Even as I speak, I'm recording footage\Nof your entire meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.21,0:07:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The first thing you discussed\Nwas Hatori's death.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.55,0:07:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you're debating who to kill next.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.39,0:07:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.26,0:07:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,[Namikawa] He's been watching everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.35,0:08:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,If you are not Kira,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.43,0:08:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,or if you are not someone\Nwho can contact Kira directly,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.15,0:08:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,let's make a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.56,0:08:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,[Namikawa] A deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.40,0:08:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] I need you to delay the deaths\Nof ELF's president
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.36,0:08:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and Mr. Zenzai by one month.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.53,0:08:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I doubt it will be difficult for someone\Nof your standing to accomplish that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.41,0:08:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,[Namikawa] Yes, yes, I see.\NRight. Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.58,0:08:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] If you complete your end\Nof the deal
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.25,0:08:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and cooperate with our requests\Nfrom now on, then your crimes--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.13,0:08:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not just yours, but everyone's crimes\Nwith the exception of Kira
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.63,0:08:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,will be parked, based on the premise\Nthat Kira blackmailed you
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.67,0:08:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,into participating in these meetings.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.88,0:08:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.34,0:08:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,[Namikawa] My only option is to join L.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.14,0:08:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'll be dead if Kira manages\Nto find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.22,0:08:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.06,0:08:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,If you tell the others about this call,\Nthey will panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.19,0:08:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be no advantage to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.23,0:08:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone would be arrested immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.78,0:08:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's not my intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.32,0:08:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm planning to go one on one\Nagainst Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.32,0:08:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen. If I win against Kira,\Nyou'll be acquitted of all charges.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.49,0:09:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,If Kira wins, then you'll be free\Nto carry on with your comfortable life.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.75,0:09:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Just play along with both parties.\NStaying on the sidelines will be best.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.50,0:09:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not in a position to lose anything\Nregardless of who wins in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.59,0:09:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You would only be at a loss if I decided\Nto arrest you right here and now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.72,0:09:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,[Namikawa] Damn it. He already knew\Nwhat answer I would've given.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.39,0:09:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] That's all for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.52,0:09:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. I'll see you Monday, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.06,0:09:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on, Namikawa?\NWho was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.36,0:09:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,One of my men screwed up again.\NI'll have to fix it on Monday.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.19,0:09:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, sorry for the interruption.\NLet's get back on topic.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.28,0:09:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We were discussing when we should kill\NZenzai and the men from ELF.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.41,0:09:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's what I'm thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.79,0:09:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll give Coil one month\Nto reveal L's identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.08,0:09:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,If he still hasn't uncovered\Nthe information we need,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.50,0:09:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,then we can go ahead\Nand kill the targets randomly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.38,0:09:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, we'll give him another month\Nto investigate and repeat the process.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.76,0:09:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Once we get rid of L permanently,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.51,0:10:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,we can go back to killing\Ntwo or three people a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.56,0:10:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, our top priority\Nshould be the elimination of L.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.81,0:10:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.23,0:10:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Once we kill L, there won't be anything\Nstanding in our way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.65,0:10:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But until then, we need to be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.73,0:10:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. Sounds like a reasonable plan\Nto me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.53,0:10:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to be extremely careful\Nif we don't wanna get caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.37,0:10:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ooi] Then we're in agreement.\NWe'll give Coil one month.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.62,0:10:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,[Yotsuba Group] Agreed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.33,0:10:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,[Namikawa] L, this should satisfy you\Nfor now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.54,0:10:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ooi] We'll still be meeting\Non a weekly basis. That is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.25,0:10:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] That went well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.88,0:10:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.88,0:10:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You really are quite amazing, Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.51,0:10:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Not only did you manage\Nto delay the killings,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.26,0:10:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,but you also set up Namikawa\Nas a potential mole for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.01,0:10:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounded exactly like the sort of thing\NI would do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.68,0:10:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And you thought of it quicker than I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.65,0:10:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.02,0:10:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,if I end up dying somehow,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.36,0:10:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,it's quite possible that you would be\Ncapable of succeeding me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.78,0:11:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Why are you being so morbid?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.36,0:11:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,There isn't time for that. We only have\Na month to figure out Kira's identity
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.16,0:11:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,and gather evidence against him\Nto prove it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.00,0:11:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,This is only the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.83,0:11:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] Yes…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.29,0:11:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But you were the one who first noticed\Nthe connection between Yotsuba and Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.59,0:11:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You actually might be more capable\Nthan I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.63,0:11:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I honestly believe you could take this on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.47,0:11:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.76,0:11:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] Tell me. If I should die…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.01,0:11:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,would you take over from me as L?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.02,0:11:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.79,0:11:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] If I should die,\Nwould you take over for me as L?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.75,0:12:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If he is Kira and just playing innocent,\Nhe's sure to say yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.01,0:12:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.72,0:12:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as we're joined by these,\Nwe would die together anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.64,0:12:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.81,0:12:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryuzaki, I'm sorry,\Nbut I'm gonna have to tell everyone
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.90,0:12:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,-what you're really thinking right now.\N-[Matsuda gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.23,0:12:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] He thinks that if I am Kira,\Nthen there are two possibilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.65,0:12:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm either just pretending I'm not him\Nand putting on an act,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.36,0:12:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,or that Kira's power has passed on\Nfrom me to someone else,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.83,0:12:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,and I have no memory\Nthat I was ever Kira in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.00,0:12:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,He's trying to determine which,\Nif either, is the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.50,0:12:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The first theory,\Nif I am putting on an act,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.79,0:12:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,he will never remove these handcuffs.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.46,0:12:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,No, even if it wasn't pretending\Nto be innocent,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.84,0:12:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure he still wouldn't take them off.\NRyuzaki still believes that I'm Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.51,0:12:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if that power had been passed\Nto someone else,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.18,0:12:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,he thinks that I would have planned
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.68,0:12:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,to have it return to me once I'm safe\Nfrom suspicion.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.15,0:12:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words,\NI wasn't being controlled at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.98,0:13:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,He thinks it was a plan,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.69,0:13:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,to pass on the power and arrange for it\Nto come back to me once I'd been cleared.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.66,0:13:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] Impressive. You figured out exactly\Nwhat I'd been thinking all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.83,0:13:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Ryuzaki's theory\Nis that once I steal L's title,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.46,0:13:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I will become Kira again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.17,0:13:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.13,0:13:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Taking on the identity of L,\Nhaving the power to control the police
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.63,0:13:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,in every country\Nwhile being Kira in secret...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.84,0:13:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's ideal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.97,0:13:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're thinking I could do it.\NNo, that I would do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.10,0:13:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what you're saying, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.93,0:13:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.31,0:13:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light breathes sharply]\NBut what about now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.06,0:13:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you, I don't want your title.\NThat should prove, even to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.98,0:13:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,that I'm not putting on an act,\Nshouldn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.98,0:13:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] If this is all an act\Nand you are trying to steal my identity,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.99,0:13:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,there's no chance you'd be foolish enough\Nto reveal your plan in front of everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.99,0:13:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,-Wouldn't you agree?\N-[Light exhales]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.95,0:13:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Ryuzaki…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.71,0:13:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.08,0:14:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think that I'm actually capable\Nof becoming a murderer?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.71,0:14:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.30,0:14:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Even after I helped you catch him?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.67,0:14:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I seem like that kind of person to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.64,0:14:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] Yes, you do. I've always thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.89,0:14:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,[both gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.03,0:14:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,[groans] Not again!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.44,0:14:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, break it up! Once is enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.90,0:14:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a draw, so let's just leave it\Nas an even match, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.82,0:14:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,[sighs] Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.58,0:14:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, let's focus on catching\Nthe Kira that's in front of us right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.50,0:14:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as I have the handcuffs on,\Nyou shouldn't have any complaints.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.46,0:14:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose so. We only have a month,\Nso there's no time to get distracted.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.34,0:14:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[Matsuda sighs in relief]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.46,0:14:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,-Ryuzaki...\N-Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.09,0:14:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[Soichiro] We have plenty\Nof footage from this meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.30,0:14:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't we use that as evidence\Nagainst those seven men
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.55,0:14:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and prevent the murders\Nof other criminals?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.76,0:14:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] Here we go again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.89,0:14:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,-Unfortunately, no.\N-But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.23,0:15:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,At the moment, we're not certain\Nif Kira is among those seven men.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.90,0:15:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,If all they have\Nis a tenuous connection with him,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.02,0:15:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,then Kira will kill them\Nas soon as they're arrested.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.19,0:15:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to be absolutely sure\Nthat Kira is among them,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.82,0:15:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,so there's no point in detaining them now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.24,0:15:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And even if it does turn out\Nto be one of them,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.20,0:15:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,it will still be quite difficult\Nto determine who the culprit is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.50,0:15:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm, I believe it's still far too early\Nfor us to make our move.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.33,0:15:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on. At the same time, we can't say\Nthat he's definitely not among the seven.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.55,0:15:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That means there's a chance\Nthe killings will stop
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.76,0:15:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,if we take this opportunity\Nto arrest them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.26,0:15:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I think Dad's right. There is a chance.\NWe have to act on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.18,0:15:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, but I think from now on,\NI should go after Kira by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.02,0:15:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.10,0:15:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You can use these headquarters,\Nas you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.40,0:15:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll also be here,\Nbut we will be working independently.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.23,0:15:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You can conduct your investigation\Nunder your own direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.07,0:15:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Feel free to arrest those men if you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.28,0:15:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I will be carrying on\Nmy own investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.66,0:15:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll only get into arguments if we don't\Nsplit up and act separately at this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.12,0:15:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,This is for the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.62,0:15:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,[Soichiro] Are you saying\Nyou're going to figure out
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.45,0:16:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,who Kira is by any means necessary?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.21,0:16:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] Yes. This case will never be solved\Nunless we capture Kira himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.71,0:16:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get me wrong. I wouldn't say\Nthat preventing deaths is pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.88,0:16:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But if we don't uncover the entire truth,\Nonce and for all,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.34,0:16:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Kira will only appear again and the number\Nof victims will continue to increase.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.97,0:16:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I believe it's more important\Nto try and find out who Kira really is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.90,0:16:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,As I've been saying,\NI'm opposed to arresting those seven men.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.19,0:16:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to do so, then you will have\Nto take responsibility for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.86,0:16:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I will pursue Kira on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.41,0:16:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,We only have one month.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.03,0:16:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder who will succeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.04,0:16:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[stammering] Ryuzaki. Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.12,0:16:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] To Amane's room.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.33,0:16:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I know you're on your father's side\Nin all this,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.75,0:16:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,but I can't remove these handcuffs.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.75,0:16:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid you're gonna have\Nto come along with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.22,0:16:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,[Misa humming]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.47,0:16:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[door opening]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.18,0:17:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps] Light! I didn't know we were\Nsupposed to have a date!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.14,0:17:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right. I should have known.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.27,0:17:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,-Misa Amane.\N-[Light grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.98,0:17:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me, do you love Light\Nfrom the bottom of your heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.11,0:17:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.40,0:17:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,-Yeah! Of course I do.\N-But you also worship Kira, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.24,0:17:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.61,0:17:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So, then. If you had to choose\Nbetween Light and Kira,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.37,0:17:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,-who would you pick?\N-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.87,0:17:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That's obvious.\NOf course it's gonna be Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.41,0:17:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really grateful to Kira and want\Nto meet him someday in person,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.54,0:17:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,but that's not true love.\NI definitely choose Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.83,0:17:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But your precious Light is planning\Nto catch Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.13,0:17:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.42,0:17:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,-Well yes, of course I am.\N-[Misa yelps]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.55,0:17:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,He says he wants to catch Kira.\NNow what will you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.72,0:17:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if that's what Light says,\Nthen I'm gonna support him no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.60,0:17:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.72,0:17:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,So, if you were given the opportunity\Nto work with Light on this investigation,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.48,0:17:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,-would you take the offer?\N-What? Ryuzaki--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.56,0:17:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Of course I would.\NI'd do anything I could to help Light!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.11,0:17:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait. Hold on a second.\NWhere are you going with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.82,0:17:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] I'm planning to have Aiber\Npose as Eraldo Coil again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.95,0:18:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll tell the Yotsuba members\Nthat while he was investigating L,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.91,0:18:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,he discovered that Misa Amane\Nmight know who he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.66,0:18:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll also tell them that L brought her\Nin for questioning
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.42,0:18:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,on the suspicion that she was\Nthe second Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.58,0:18:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[Misa] That part is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.25,0:18:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,If the Yotsuba Group believes that Misa\Ncould be their lead to finding L,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.26,0:18:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,then they'll say\Nthat they want to meet her
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.97,0:18:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,to discuss their advertising campaign.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.93,0:18:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll use that opportunity\Nto question her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.55,0:18:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to Matsuda's screw up,\Nthey may already be considering Misa
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.81,0:18:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,as their new spokesperson,\Nso this could work.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.27,0:18:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.60,0:18:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,-We can't do that.\N-Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.98,0:18:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,This plan is too risky.\NWho knows what could happen to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.61,0:18:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps] Oh, wow. Does that mean\Nyou're worried about me? Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.90,0:18:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't worry.\NI won't mind doing something like this
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.37,0:18:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,if it's for you, Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.03,0:18:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, Misa. If they suspect\Nthat you might know who L really is,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.00,0:18:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,we don't know how far they'll be willing\Nto go to get that information.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.21,0:18:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,No problemo. I promise I won't\Nsay anything, even if they torture me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.34,0:18:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I can attest to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.21,0:18:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But Kira can control his victim's actions\Nbefore their death.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.30,0:19:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a good chance\Nhe might try to manipulate her
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.55,0:19:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,into revealing what she knows\Nand then kill her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.43,0:19:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, if he does manage to kill L,\Nhe won't have any use for Misa.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.39,0:19:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,He'd kill her to keep her silent.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.85,0:19:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like the sound of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.56,0:19:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,-[L] Light.\N-Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.81,0:19:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You forget that if we win against Kira,\NMisa won't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.28,0:19:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, as long as we're handcuffed\Ntogether, you and I share the same fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.24,0:19:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,If I die, so will you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.12,0:19:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,[Misa whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.24,0:19:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] If that happens, Misa is the one\Nwho would grieve most of all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.41,0:19:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Either we lose and both die together,\Nor we successfully catch Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.54,0:19:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Which is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.58,0:19:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We catch Kira! I would never dream\Nabout living in a world without Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.51,0:19:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,-Yes, that would be dark.\N-Cut it out. This is just crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.68,0:19:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We're running out of time\Nand I'm starting to get desperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.72,0:19:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,As for Misa Amane, I've turned to her\Nbecause I know her bravery
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.52,0:19:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and love for you is boundless.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.81,0:19:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really mean it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.10,0:19:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no. I think I've totally\Nmisunderstood you all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.07,0:19:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I even called you a pervert.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.07,0:20:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But you actually do understand\Nhow I feel, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.36,0:20:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Misa is indisputably the most perfect\Nand worthy woman for Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.33,0:20:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.33,0:20:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You're such a sweetie. Thank you, Ryuzaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.87,0:20:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I could actually fall for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.54,0:20:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[Misa] Let's not go that far.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.79,0:20:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But you could maybe be a friend of mine.\NWould that be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.67,0:20:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. So now I've gained\Nyet another friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.76,0:20:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Of course, any friend of Light's\Nis a friend of mine as well. [laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.76,0:20:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,-Let's all be friends together!\N-[L] Yay, fun...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.02,0:20:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course, I would never think\Nof betraying any of my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.27,0:20:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,With our powers combined,\Nwe'll arrest Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.32,0:20:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,-[L] Unfortunately...\N-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.74,0:20:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Light's taking a different\Ninvestigative approach from us
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.07,0:20:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and will be working with his father\Nand the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.36,0:20:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,-[Light] Huh?\N-[L] I'm afraid it'll just be you and I.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.83,0:20:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What's up with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.49,0:20:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, L, now you're just playing dirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.91,0:20:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You're leaving me with no other choice\Nbut to join your--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.42,0:20:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] No, that's quite all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.92,0:20:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[Misa] What are you talking about?\NOf course he'll be joining us!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.88,0:21:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not it either.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.34,0:21:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been opposed to this investigation\Nsince the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.01,0:21:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,-It's too dangerous for her.\N-Oh, Light…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.84,0:21:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so sweet.\NThank you for worrying about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.89,0:21:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But please let me do this.\NI wanna be useful to you somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.81,0:21:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,If I can be useful,\Nthen maybe you'll love me even more.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.56,0:21:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And besides, I would gladly die\Nif it were for you, Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.90,0:21:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,[Soichiro] Figuring out the logistics\Nof arresting seven people
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.32,0:21:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,is going to be challenging.\NI don't suppose you two have any ideas?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.16,0:21:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Mogi? Matsuda?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.78,0:21:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,TO BE CONTINUED
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.00,0:21:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[theme music playing]